OL,3,CCumbria hosts World Marmalade Awards
OL,4,Cas 3,400 entries submitted
OL,6,FA passionfruit and Seville orange
OL,7,Fpreserve has won top prize at the
OL,8,FWorld Marmalade Awards held in Cumbria.
OL,10,FIt was created by David Hinkins from
OL,11,FSomerset who beat off 3,400 other
OL,12,Fentries from across the globe to claim
OL,13,Fthe honour.
OL,15,FThe annual event takes place at
OL,16,FDalemain Mansion near Penrith and
OL,17,Fattracts competitors and vistors from
OL,18,Fas far afield as Hong Kong and
OL,19,FSwaziland.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
