FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1777395954
OL,3,CCumbria hosts World Marmalade Awards
OL,4,Cas 3,400 entries submitted
OL,6,FDavid Hinkins' winning preserve is now
OL,7,Fon sale with a percentage from each
OL,8,Fjar going to Hospice at Home.
OL,10,FHe said: "I can't believe it! It's
OL,11,Fbeen fun for the last 11 years,
OL,12,Fgetting that little bit better every
OL,13,Fyear and helping such a worthy cause
OL,14,Falong the way."
OL,16,FBeatrice Hasell-McCosh, Director of
OL,17,FThe Dalemain World Marmalade Awards,
OL,18,Fsaid: "It is a brilliant win for David
OL,19,FHinkins, who has been entering the
OL,20,Fcompetition for years.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1777395954
OL,3,CCumbria hosts World Marmalade Awards
OL,4,Cas 3,400 entries submitted
OL,6,F"This year marks our 21st anniversary
OL,7,Fand so a passionfruit marmalade seems
OL,8,Fhugely appropriate for those who feel
OL,9,Fpassionate about this much loved
OL,10,Fpreserve!"
OL,12,FDebbie Mkenna, CEO of Hospice at Home
OL,13,FCarlisle and North Lakeland said: "We
OL,14,Fwere delighted to be part again in
OL,15,Fthis year's Dalemain Marmalade
OL,16,FFestival and would like to thank the
OL,17,Forganisers, volunteers and everyone
OL,18,Fwho attended for their incredible and
OL,19,Fcontinued support.
OL,26,@uD@cOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/5
