OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1777395954
OL,3,CCumbria hosts World Marmalade Awards
OL,4,Cas 3,400 entries submitted
OL,6,F"The event once again showcased the
OL,7,Fwarmth, creativity and community
OL,8,Fspirit that Cumbria is known for.
OL,10,F"It was a pleasure to meet so many
OL,11,Fvisitors and share more about the work
OL,12,FHospice at Home Carlisle & North
OL,13,FLakeland provides to patients and
OL,14,Ffamilies across our region.
OL,16,F"Events like this make a real
OL,17,Fdifference, helping us continue to
OL,18,Fdeliver compassionate hospice care in
OL,19,Fthe comfort of people's own homes
OL,20,Fwithin our local community."
